11:01.320 --> 11:07.520
And you can basically estimate how big a fraction of your objects that seem to be authentic.

11:08.540 --> 11:11.160
Of course, what do we do?

11:11.340 --> 11:12.040
We test this.

11:12.260 --> 11:12.480
Yes.

11:12.600 --> 11:15.540
Because we have this code from a guy called Guineer.

11:15.900 --> 11:17.420
