27:25.200 --> 27:27.460
about the historic and scientific record.

27:27.920 --> 27:30.580
These two quote-unquote natural satellites

27:30.580 --> 27:33.620
never show up again in any of the literature

27:33.620 --> 27:35.880
on asteroids and near-Earth objects.

27:36.340 --> 27:37.880
Given that the moon is regarded

27:37.880 --> 27:40.380
as the Earth's only permanent natural satellite,

27:40.880 --> 27:43.000
