36:10.400 --> 36:11.560
I got training

36:11.560 --> 36:13.080
in research design,

36:13.640 --> 36:14.520
statistics

36:14.520 --> 36:15.880
and have practiced

36:15.880 --> 36:16.400
that,

36:16.600 --> 36:16.760
you know,

36:16.800 --> 36:17.660
the research skills

36:17.660 --> 36:18.320
and statistics

36:18.320 --> 36:19.440
