39:17.260 --> 39:17.900
a lot of those

39:17.900 --> 39:19.220
nuclear tests.

39:19.220 --> 39:21.960
But, yeah,

39:22.220 --> 39:23.340
that's fascinating.

39:23.520 --> 39:24.240
Is there any way

39:24.240 --> 39:25.240
