39:34.780 --> 39:35.420
kind of,

39:36.020 --> 39:36.920
looking at general

39:36.920 --> 39:37.520
directions,

39:37.520 --> 39:39.060
because all of these

39:39.060 --> 39:39.980
that we've looked at

39:39.980 --> 39:41.140
