40:13.760 --> 40:14.600
to do that, though.

40:15.080 --> 40:15.680
This would be

40:15.680 --> 40:17.920
a really big deal,

40:17.920 --> 40:18.360
I think,

40:18.460 --> 40:19.580
if, you know,

40:19.880 --> 40:21.560
the entire consensus

40:21.560 --> 40:22.660
sort of accepted it,

40:22.700 --> 40:24.040
because already

40:24.040 --> 40:24.840
