40:25.860 --> 40:26.580
documenting

40:26.580 --> 40:28.420
160-plus

40:28.420 --> 40:29.300
queue-cleared

40:29.300 --> 40:31.180
ICBM security personnel,

40:31.340 --> 40:32.140
radar operators,

40:32.460 --> 40:33.780
guys at nuclear bases

40:33.780 --> 40:35.180
with no incentive

40:35.180 --> 40:36.040
