40:36.180 --> 40:37.260
no histrionic

40:37.260 --> 40:38.080
streak

40:38.080 --> 40:39.100
in their personalities.

40:39.820 --> 40:40.720
Often they're tested,

40:40.940 --> 40:41.360
actually,

40:41.880 --> 40:43.560
for being sound of mind.

40:43.660 --> 40:44.240
They're on what's called

40:44.240 --> 40:44.840
the PRP,

40:44.840 --> 40:46.360
