40:47.240 --> 40:48.560
They have to be inherently,

40:48.760 --> 40:49.040
you know,

40:49.100 --> 40:50.100
kind of credible witnesses,

40:50.460 --> 40:51.860
and they're all seeing UFOs.

40:52.200 --> 40:53.980
And what your study does

40:53.980 --> 40:54.580
is it almost

40:54.580 --> 40:56.260
implies,

40:56.640 --> 40:57.120
possibly,

40:57.420 --> 40:58.560
that these are coming

40:58.560 --> 40:59.680
from space.

40:59.860 --> 41:01.660
They're not just showing up,

41:01.860 --> 41:02.760
you know,

41:03.000 --> 41:03.380
locally

41:03.380 --> 41:05.240
at the Air Force base.

41:05.940 --> 41:06.040
Yeah,

41:06.120 --> 41:06.980
so here's the pieces

41:06.980 --> 41:07.860
of information

41:07.860 --> 41:09.700
that I like to point out

41:09.700 --> 41:10.520
when I'm talking

41:10.520 --> 41:11.600
